These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, pony, mouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, yellow, red, lilac
City: london, paris, nizza, new-york
4 different games are played: monopoly, domino, whist, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, subway, van
 1. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 8. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5
 9. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
11. the person playing domino is the person driving the car##1
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
13. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
14. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5
15. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the person traveling to new-york##7
16. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
17. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
18. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
19. the owner of the mouse is not the person traveling to new-york##6
20. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
21. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |      3      |      4      |
| Pet      | cat  | mouse          | pony       | bird         |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | reading      | video-games | card-games  |
| Color           | red  | lilac | blue       | yellow |
| City   | london    | paris         | nizza      | new-york        |
| Game   | bridge      | whist     | domino      | monopoly   |
| Transport     | van          | motorbike    | car         | subway      |

